/#
 Specifies the fallback provisions in respect to the applicable Futures Price Valuation.
 #/
enum FpML5.recordkeeping.FPVFinalPriceElectionFallbackEnum {
    # In respect of the Early Final Valuation Date, the provisions for FPV Close shall apply.
    FPVClose 
    # In respect of the Early Final Valuation Date, the provisions for FPV Hedge Execution shall apply.
    FPVHedgeExecution 

}

FPVClose.Doc: In respect of the Early Final Valuation Date, the provisions for FPV Close shall apply.
FPVClose.Name: FPVClose

FPVHedgeExecution.Doc: In respect of the Early Final Valuation Date, the provisions for FPV Hedge Execution shall apply.
FPVHedgeExecution.Name: FPVHedgeExecution
